sec.title: Print Subscription Discount for the Attendees of Partnering Conferences
sec.p: Bentham Science is pleased to offer 20% discount on the listed rates for 2019 subscriptions to the attendees of partnering conferences. The list of conferences can be viewed at https://benthamscience.com/partnering-events/
If you are attending any of these partnering conferences & wish to avail Bentham Science discount offer please write to marketing@benthamscience.net or subscriptions@benthamscience.net
For further information on this offer, write to marketing@benthamscience.net
